OL,3,CProperties evacuated after
OL,4,C'potentially hazardous chemicals' found
OL,6,FA number of properties have been
OL,7,Fevacuated and a number of roads have
OL,8,Fbeen closed after potentially
OL,9,Fhazardous chemicals were found at a
OL,10,Fbusiness premises near Derby city
OL,11,Fcentre.
OL,13,FPolice say they received a report just
OL,14,Fafter 10.30am this morning about the
OL,15,Fchemicals being found at a premises in
OL,16,FMidland Road.
OL,18,FThey were found during routine work at
OL,19,Fa business in the area with police
OL,20,Fsaying no criminal matters have been
OL,21,Finitiated.
