OL,3,CProperties evacuated after
OL,4,C'potentially hazardous chemicals' found
OL,6,FA 100-metre cordon around the business
OL,7,Fhas been put up as a "precautionary
OL,8,Fmeasure" while emergency services
OL,9,Frespond to the incident.
OL,11,FRoads which are closed or partially
OL,12,Fclosed include:
OL,14,FOfficers at Derbyshire Police say they
OL,15,Fare also liaising with staff at
OL,16,FCastleward Spencer Academy, part of
OL,17,Fwhich is inside the cordon. Staff and
OL,18,Fstudents have been advised to stay
OL,19,Finside for the time being.
